{"tid":2382471,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"而家連村屋私了淋油都要學攬炒巴style","createTime":"2021-01-27T09:52:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T18:33:28.000Z","uid":7439,"like":7,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7dddb1fa890c93af3671ae16fe75cf5e6d79dbbb","tid":2382471,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T09:52:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20210127/s00001/9834b19fc9fd24479c1bb2920a13d73b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20210127%2Fs00001%2F9834b19fc9fd24479c1bb2920a13d73b.jpg&h=b8f587ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早上8時42分，屯門藍地大街屯門新村有3間村屋分別被淋油，村內3輛私家車亦遭人淋潑起漆水刑毁，有村民發現報警，警方正調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">現場消息指出，被淋油的村屋為屯門新村村長陶兆林及其2名兒子的寓所</span><span class=\"orange\">，其中陶兆林的村屋大閘被淋黃色油漆，外牆被淋橙色油漆，其2名兒子的村屋則被淋上橙、綠和紅油，被淋起漆水刑毁的私家車亦為3人的座駕。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">73歲的陶兆林表示，屯門新村曾發生多次同類刑毁案，他多年來與家族成員有土地糾紛</span><span class=\"orange\">，2015年時亦曾遇襲，他估計有人欲透過刑毁向他施壓，逼使他不再介入家族土地糾紛。</span><br />\n<br />\n根據村長提供的閉路電視片段，凌晨近4時有3名身穿深色衣物的蒙面男子闖入村內，向3間村屋及3部私家車刑毁，歷時約2分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n警方把案件列刑事毁壞，屯門警區刑事調查隊第4隊接手跟進，正追緝兩名年約20至30歲、案發時身穿深色外套、戴口罩和帽的的本地男子歸案。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20210127/s00001/1611727342310/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E6%96%B0%E6%9D%91%E6%9D%91%E9%95%B7%E7%88%B6%E5%AD%90%E5%AF%93%E6%89%80%E9%81%AD%E6%B7%8B%E6%B2%B9-%E4%B8%89%E5%BA%A7%E9%A7%95%E5%90%8C%E9%81%AD%E6%B7%8B%E8%B5%B7%E6%BC%86%E6%B0%B4%E5%88%91%E6%AF%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20210127%2Fs00001%2F1611727342310%2F%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%259D%2591%25E6%259D%2591%25E9%2595%25B7%25E7%2588%25B6%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25AF%2593%25E6%2589%2580%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%25B7%258B%25E6%25B2%25B9-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25BA%25A7%25E9%25A7%2595%25E5%2590%258C%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%25B7%258B%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E6%25BC%2586%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%2588%2591%25E6%25AF%2581&d=vmCIlZEHEchodQF1AoZdn%2B2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=57951c1a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20210127%2Fs00001%2F1611727342310%2F%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%259D%2591%25E6%259D%2591%25E9%2595%25B7%25E7%2588%25B6%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25AF%2593%25E6%2589%2580%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%25B7%258B%25E6%25B2%25B9-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25BA%25A7%25E9%25A7%2595%25E5%2590%258C%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%25B7%258B%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E6%25BC%2586%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%2588%2591%25E6%25AF%2581&h=62ce5f4d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20210127/s00001/1611727342310/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E6%96%B0%E6%9D%91%E6%9D%91%E9%95%B7%E7%88%B6%E5%AD%90%E5%AF%93%E6%89%80%E9%81%AD%E6%B7%8B%E6%B2%B9-%E4%B8%89%E5%BA%A7%E9%A7%95%E5%90%8C%E9%81%AD%E6%B7%8B%E8%B5%B7%E6%BC%86%E6%B0%B4%E5%88%91%E6%AF%81</a>"},{"pid":"0d2e4d7076da0f4d31609a9c4a6f8443532ef2ef","tid":2382471,"uid":220451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T09:54:20.000Z","msg":"啊偉係度嗎？"},{"pid":"f928d69bae0be3336c41b4a444343846f696a0e6","tid":2382471,"uid":311626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T10:03:39.000Z","msg":"攬抄之色"},{"pid":"82ed458d7d5173ff914172329eabcfde73ada450","tid":2382471,"uid":38189,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T10:05:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMGTfOeA.gif&amp;h=11bf4274&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"eee1ced96605f155042f647fb06cc9e0bc2afe25","tid":2382471,"uid":7439,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"82ed458d7d5173ff914172329eabcfde73